</tr>
</table>
</center>

</p><p>
Our previous hardware platform is the <b>Pluto</b> mote, designed here at Harvard,
which is a scaled-down
version of the Telos designed to be small, lightweight, and wearable.
The Pluto incorporates a tiny, rechargeable Li-ion battery, 
small USB connector, and 3-axis accelerometer.

</p><p>
<center>
<table border=0 hspace=0 cellspacing=10 width="80%">
